                     <interp inst="t18250519-169-off983" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250519-169-cd984" type="crimeDate">11th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250519-169-off983 t18250519-169-cd984"></join>, a watch, value 15 s.; a seal, value 5 s.; a key, value 1 d., and a ribbon, value 1 d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250519-169-victim884" type="victimName">
                        James 
                        Spear
                     <interp inst="t18250519-169-victim884" type="surname" value="Spear"></interp>
